00:13:59,327 --> 00:14:01,540
nor ikh fleg in algemeyn,

229
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:04,615
ven me hot gemakht KOTLITN,

230
00:14:04,635 --> 00:14:08,460
hob ikh azoy lang gepatsht, biz ikh hob a shtikl aropgepatsht,

