00:14:36,849 --> 00:14:40,201
host mir dort aruntergeleygt a sh- a shtikl fleysh. zog ikh,

238
00:14:40,832 --> 00:14:44,083
to- tomer se iz tsu fil, breng es tsurik.

239
00:14:44,645 --> 00:14:46,161
vel ikh shoyn,

240
00:14:46,161 --> 00:14:47,694
vet es mir oykh shmekn.

