249
00:15:07,145 --> 00:15:09,379
iz azoy ho'mir zikh a eytse gegebn.

250
00:15:11,409 --> 00:15:14,036
biz, ikh gedenk nisht velkhe monat se gevezn,

251
00:15:14,177 --> 00:15:17,141
ober se hot shoyn ongehoybn in droysn

252
00:15:18,598 --> 00:15:20,060
tsu frirn.

253
00:15:24,487 --> 00:15:26,152
hob ikh demolts

254
00:15:28,638 --> 00:15:32,952
mayne ratsyon gezamlt,

255
00:15:33,228 --> 00:15:35,534
vayl ikh hob nisht gedarft der,

256
00:15:35,692 --> 00:15:37,782
vayl ikh hob gegesn dort genug.

257
00:15:37,818 --> 00:15:44,039
der mayn ratsyon hob ikh tsamgenumen un ikh hob es imer getrogn tsu mayn bruder, tsu di khaveyrim fun der heym, azoy vayter.

258
00:15:45,395 --> 00:15:49,524
un varsheynlekh hot er, hot im vayter oysgefelt epes andersh,

259
00:15:49,580 --> 00:15:50,789
dem kapo,

260
00:15:51,015 --> 00:15:52,849
fun di kokh, dem oyteman,

261
00:15:53,799 --> 00:15:56,628
iz hot er mikh gekhapt az ikh,

262
00:15:57,140 --> 00:16:00,648
se ofitsyel iz es gevezn, ober

263
00:16:00,648 --> 00:16:03,159
hot er gezogt az ikh hob do geganvet,

264
00:16:03,924 --> 00:16:06,686
hob ikh gekrign finef un tsvontsik

265
00:16:07,147 --> 00:16:08,998
un dos iz gegangen shoyn

266
00:16:11,248 --> 00:16:14,026
akht tog shoynung,

267
00:16:15,247 --> 00:16:17,303
shpital, ikh meyn shoynung,

268
00:16:17,340 --> 00:16:20,271
un nakher hot men mikh geshikt oyf SHTRAFE lager.

269
00:16:20,428 --> 00:16:22,957
bin ikh gegangen arbetn bay

270
00:16:22,957 --> 00:16:24,658
o- oyf di boy-shtele,

271
00:16:25,592 --> 00:16:27,611
vu men hot gemakht,

272
00:16:28,275 --> 00:16:29,771
fun a tol,

273
00:16:30,384 --> 00:16:32,117
hot men ongefilt,

274
00:16:32,730 --> 00:16:38,276
gemakht a SHTRASE. di SHTRASE is geendikt gevorn, NACH UNK dorf tsum banhoyf,

275
00:16:41,454 --> 00:16:45,195
un dort hot men geboyt

276
00:16:45,285 --> 00:16:46,410
a tunel.

277
00:16:46,736 --> 00:16:49,751
fun dem tunel vos me hot aroysgenumen, in di berg,

278
00:16:50,347 --> 00:16:55,117
hobn z- mashinen gearbet, un se geven a groyse rash un azoy vayter.

279
00:16:55,713 --> 00:17:02,677
nu, ikh bin aroysgekumen, hobn zey mikh zeyer gut gekent, di vekhter, di di di WEHRMACHT oder di S.S. ZOGAR,

280
00:17:03,155 --> 00:17:03,976
UNK,

281
00:17:04,320 --> 00:17:07,487
hobn zey zikh gevundert vos ikh kum, " vos makhstu HIER?"

282
00:17:07,947 --> 00:17:10,152
zogt er, "du bist NICHT mer in di KUCHE?"

283
00:17:10,344 --> 00:17:11,312
zog ikh,

284
00:17:11,312 --> 00:17:13,831
"ICH HAB tsu fil ge⟨UNK⟩ VIELLEICHT,

285
00:17:14,124 --> 00:17:15,975
hot er mikh aroysgeshmisn."

286
00:17:17,297 --> 00:17:20,278
zogt er, hobn zey mir gezogt, "makh dir keyn zorgn.

287
00:17:20,638 --> 00:17:23,636
es vet dir GORNIKS pasirn HIER."

288
00:17:27,557 --> 00:17:29,003
her ikh azoy,

289
00:17:29,379 --> 00:17:31,790
un ikh hob gearbet take. se geven kalt,

290
00:17:31,790 --> 00:17:33,356
ikh bin yung gevezn,

291
00:17:33,615 --> 00:17:36,917
opgeshvakht bin ikh nisht gevezn azoy vi andere,

292
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:41,524
un di vagonlekh vos me hot gebrengt,

293
00:17:42,930 --> 00:17:44,241
di LOREN,

294
00:17:44,685 --> 00:17:46,097
hobn zikh geboygn,

295
00:17:46,271 --> 00:17:48,662
me hot gedarft mit a brekh-shtange

296
00:17:49,308 --> 00:17:54,454
gut oyf a plats UNK, hot zikh dos ibergekert un dos in dem lokh arayn.

297
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:57,929
un mir hot men dertseylt, ikh hob gevust, nor ikh hob es nisht

298
00:17:57,977 --> 00:18:00,693
perzenlekh gezen, hob ikh es nisht azoy gefilt.

299
00:18:01,155 --> 00:18:03,962
az dort do der

300
00:18:04,007 --> 00:18:06,026
oyfzeer fun der arbet,

301
00:18:07,213 --> 00:18:08,557
a shleziyer,

302
00:18:09,592 --> 00:18:11,665
heysn heyst er SOBOTA,

303
00:18:11,665 --> 00:18:12,826
hot er geheysn,

304
00:18:13,187 --> 00:18:18,750
er hot gehat a sistem, a gezuntn hot er krank gemakht un a kranker iz geshtorbn.

305
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:26,259
iz ven ikh bin gekumen tsu der arbet dort, zogt mikh eyner fun di S. S.,

306
00:18:26,433 --> 00:18:27,862
"her SOBOTA,

307
00:18:27,986 --> 00:18:29,432
HIER hobn ZI

308
00:18:29,673 --> 00:18:31,434
direkt fun di KUCHE,

309
00:18:31,445 --> 00:18:33,009
eyn gut arbeter."

310
00:18:33,504 --> 00:18:36,468
ikh hob gekukt zayn ponem, a royter iz er gevezn,

311
00:18:36,727 --> 00:18:39,337
keyn guts hob ikh nisht gezen fun im,

312
00:18:40,338 --> 00:18:42,172
un

313
00:18:42,566 --> 00:18:43,421
shoyn.

314
00:18:43,595 --> 00:18:45,581
ikh hob mikh genumen tsu arbetn,

315
00:18:46,329 --> 00:18:48,298
un ikh hob geholfn di andere,

316
00:18:49,350 --> 00:18:52,567
un ikh ze az er geyt mit a

317
00:18:52,758 --> 00:18:53,984
kroyts-hak,

318
00:18:55,246 --> 00:18:59,790
un ikh ze epes zukht er mikh, hob ikh farshtanen er vil mir gebn a klap.

319
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:03,654
shrayen, "SHNELL! HUNTER!" ikh veys er vet zogn dort, ober a klap vet er mir gebn.

320
00:19:03,744 --> 00:19:07,637
un ikh hob far a klap moyre gehat mer vi far nisht esn.

321
00:19:09,954 --> 00:19:11,872
hot es mikh denervirt,

322
00:19:12,992 --> 00:19:16,243
un ikh hob oyfgepast.

323
00:19:24,686 --> 00:19:29,130
se nokh nisht, se nokh geven, ⟨lokomotiv⟩ iz er mir gekumen, ober se nokh geven genug vayt.

324
00:19:29,130 --> 00:19:31,987
vayl se iz mer vi eyn ⟨lokomotiv⟩ dort gebrengt a,

325
00:19:32,263 --> 00:19:33,624
tse-,

326
00:19:34,052 --> 00:19:36,578
ikh gloyb tsen toyznt mentshn ho'mir dort gearbet tsu,

327
00:19:39,401 --> 00:19:40,475
iz er avek.

328
00:19:43,052 --> 00:19:45,039
bay, bay nekste mol

329
00:19:45,039 --> 00:19:52,480
hob ikh geshrign, ikh veys, "oyfgepast! di ⟨LORRY kumt er⟩." ikh hob gemakht koyles, azolkhe shrayerayen,

330
00:19:52,532 --> 00:19:54,381
az

331
00:19:55,753 --> 00:19:57,384
un dos iz gegangen

332
00:19:57,508 --> 00:19:59,530
eyns nokhn andern kimat,

333
00:19:59,567 --> 00:20:00,827
ver se ⟨gegangen⟩.

334
00:20:01,355 --> 00:20:08,302
dan ze ikh az er kumt un yetst vet nisht helfn keyn dokter oykh nisht. er muz mir gebn a klap. ober mir vet er nisht gebn.

335
00:20:09,287 --> 00:20:10,901
er kumt tsu,

336
00:20:11,683 --> 00:20:15,596
un heybt oyf un git a klap un ikh nem es, rays es aroys,

337
00:20:15,791 --> 00:20:18,231
yung un flink bin ikh nokh gevezn,

338
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:21,723
un ikh gib a nem, ikh gib a varf avek,

339
00:20:22,232 --> 00:20:30,155
un er heybt on tsu shrayen, zogt, "der hunt, der JUDE," un azoy vayter, "hot mir UNK."

340
00:20:30,836 --> 00:20:32,872
un ikh loz aroys

341
00:20:33,266 --> 00:20:35,994
a gelekhter, aza

342
00:20:36,405 --> 00:20:39,116
fun shrek, lakhn, tsuzamen.

343
00:20:40,860 --> 00:20:44,027
kumt tsu der ⟨OBERSHARFIRER⟩ fun der vakh,

344
00:20:44,842 --> 00:20:46,636
zogt er, "VOS IZ UNK."

345
00:20:46,636 --> 00:20:48,195
vos iz ge- geshen?

346
00:20:48,690 --> 00:20:52,836
ZAGT er, "der hunt hot UNK dort iz der pike VAS ikh hob im UNK."

347
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:57,460
un ikh lakh. zogt er, "shvayg!

348
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:02,760
zofort gey arayn in der bode.

349
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:05,300
du bist gefangen."

350
00:21:09,834 --> 00:21:11,313
ikh kum arayn ahin,

351
00:21:11,437 --> 00:21:15,870
in droysn hot geregnt un se gefaln shney un se geven a frost,

352
00:21:16,230 --> 00:21:17,828
ikh kum arayn, fregn zey mikh,

353
00:21:18,491 --> 00:21:23,329
vos iz? zog ikh, der der SOBOTA, un z- un zey hobn im oykh nisht lib gehat.

354
00:21:25,848 --> 00:21:29,128
iz, zog ikh, "yo, der SOBOTA

355
00:21:29,128 --> 00:21:31,411
ZAGT az ikh HOB im veln toytn."

356
00:21:32,227 --> 00:21:34,213
nu, hot men mikh arestirt.

357
00:21:34,674 --> 00:21:36,356
bin ikh.

358
00:21:37,577 --> 00:21:41,200
doyert efsher a por minut, kumt arayn der OBERSHTARFUHRER, zogt er,

359
00:21:41,458 --> 00:21:43,494
"du veyst," zogt er, "Herman,

360
00:21:44,985 --> 00:21:49,671
ikh hob shoyn gezen ven EYNE JUDE hot EYN doytshe an UNK gegebn,

361
00:21:50,098 --> 00:21:52,320
ober der iz glaykh geshosn gevorn."

362
00:21:52,629 --> 00:21:53,501
oyftu.

363
00:21:54,468 --> 00:21:55,343
"nor,

364
00:21:55,343 --> 00:21:59,981
a JUDE der lozt zikh NICHT SHLAGN, SHADE dos du JUDE bist."

365
00:22:00,527 --> 00:22:02,884
zog ikh, "dos iz mayne shikzal."

366
00:22:03,817 --> 00:22:07,136
ZAGT er, "zi, DAS IST GUT VARUM HIER IST," un er iz aroys.

367
00:22:07,952 --> 00:22:15,678
bay der nakht hot er gedarft mikh ibergebn in lager, di di me zol mikh shisn, hengen,

368
00:22:15,678 --> 00:22:18,307
ikh meyn nisht, far bashtrofn vos ikh hob do getun,

369
00:22:19,697 --> 00:22:21,970
bin ikh gekumen tsum lager eltster,

370
00:22:22,768 --> 00:22:24,517
hob ikh ge-

371
00:22:25,299 --> 00:22:28,348
neyn, ikh bin nisht gekumen demolts. shpeter gekumen.

372
00:22:29,771 --> 00:22:30,879
gornisht.

373
00:22:30,969 --> 00:22:34,068
dem nekstn tog aroysgekumen tsu der arbet vi normal,

374
00:22:34,361 --> 00:22:38,012
ikh hob gornisht gevust vos me hot gezogt, yo gezogt, ober normal hot er gedarft zogn,

375
00:22:38,012 --> 00:22:39,823
er hot gezogt, nor ikh hob nisht gevust.

376
00:22:41,178 --> 00:22:42,877
iz

377
00:22:45,043 --> 00:22:49,408
dort vu ikh bin gevezn iz gevezn menukhe.

378
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:52,816
se hot im azoy fardrosn,

379
00:22:54,358 --> 00:22:57,761
un hot efsher shoyn moyre gehat az der der

380
00:22:58,475 --> 00:23:01,839
der S. S. tuen mikh a bisl protezhirn,

381
00:23:01,884 --> 00:23:05,034
un zey hobn zeyer shlekht geven, vayl zey zenen geven JEALOUS,

382
00:23:05,580 --> 00:23:12,048
vayl zey hot men nisht genumen tsum militer. di OTE- mentshn zenen geven arbets-mentshn,

383
00:23:12,048 --> 00:23:14,242
tomer hot er gemakht a feler,

384
00:23:14,253 --> 00:23:16,930
hot men im geshikt oyfn OST-front, dos yo.

385
00:23:17,038 --> 00:23:18,731
un zey zenen gevezn,

386
00:23:18,731 --> 00:23:20,508
im hot men gekent shikn

387
00:23:21,594 --> 00:23:24,418
tsum militer, tsum tsum tsun a front oder vos,

388
00:23:24,418 --> 00:23:25,504
zey nisht.

389
00:23:25,762 --> 00:23:28,288
z- hobn zey gehat tsvishn zikh aza dos.

390
00:23:34,262 --> 00:23:36,826
dray vokhn shpeter umgefer,

391
00:23:37,271 --> 00:23:39,088
kumt a delegatsye,

392
00:23:42,097 --> 00:23:44,454
iz gevezn dort ofitsirn,

393
00:23:45,303 --> 00:23:46,752
iz gevezn eyner mit

394
00:23:46,755 --> 00:23:51,272
a, mit a halbe hant, vos se hot im gefelt, iz oykh dort gevezn,

395
00:23:52,172 --> 00:23:56,048
un zey kumen gebn premyes d- far di arbeter.

396
00:23:57,335 --> 00:23:58,868
vos iz geven premye?

397
00:23:58,905 --> 00:24:03,354
der ershte premye iz gevezn tsvey hundert ⟨UMA⟩ tsigaretn.

398
00:24:04,085 --> 00:24:05,936
dos iz gevezn a,

399
00:24:06,819 --> 00:24:14,390
a gute tsigaret, nisht keyn zeyer fayne tsigaret, ikh meyn, nisht keyn DIAMOND tsigaret, ober a gute tsigaret.

400
00:24:15,054 --> 00:24:19,908
dos iz geven der ershte, un dan iz gevezn bir bir un azelkhe zakhn.

401
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:22,035
kumt tsu der

402
00:24:22,158 --> 00:24:25,122
OBER--SHARFIRER fun der arbet,

403
00:24:25,871 --> 00:24:27,350
er iz oykh gevezn dort,

404
00:24:27,407 --> 00:24:30,371
zogt er, "dos iz der bester arbeter," tsaygt er oyf mir.

405
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:32,087
der SOBOTA

406
00:24:32,098 --> 00:24:34,489
hot zikh gevolt zikher zelbst-mordn.

407
00:24:34,865 --> 00:24:38,268
er hot gezen az ikh k- az ikh krig der ershte dos.

408
00:24:38,848 --> 00:24:39,419
shoyn.

409
00:24:39,419 --> 00:24:42,521
bin ikh arayngekumen in lager mit dem tsetl,

410
00:24:43,404 --> 00:24:49,220
bin ikh tsugegangen tsum lager eltster, zogt er, bist meshuge gevorn, zogt er, du host dokh im hersht gevolt hargenen!

411
00:24:49,766 --> 00:24:51,313
er hot gevust derfun.

412
00:24:52,128 --> 00:24:53,459
vayl der

413
00:24:53,459 --> 00:24:56,106
der OBERSHARFIRER, vi heyst es dort, hot im gezogt.

414
00:24:56,212 --> 00:24:57,374
SHAKHFIRER,

415
00:24:57,410 --> 00:24:58,721
SHAKHTFIRER.

416
00:24:59,233 --> 00:25:01,978
zogt er, zogt ikh tsu im azoy.

417
00:25:02,237 --> 00:25:04,714
KHOTSI SHELI VEKHOTSI SHELOKH

418
00:25:04,714 --> 00:25:06,736
kodesh, ikh vil nisht aroysgeyn tsu der arbet.

419
00:25:06,793 --> 00:25:09,740
zogt er, du bist dokh krank, muzt dokh geyn oyf shoynung.

420
00:25:10,691 --> 00:25:17,469
