00:25:41,673 --> 00:25:43,105
bin ikh krank gevorn.

428
00:25:43,105 --> 00:25:45,161
faktish krank gevorn.

429
00:25:46,820 --> 00:25:49,042
trots dem vos ikh hob gekrign

430
00:25:49,554 --> 00:25:52,350
aynshtekher far flek-tifus,

431
00:25:53,385 --> 00:25:54,864
bin ikh krank gevorn,

432
00:25:55,967 --> 00:25:59,252
un ikh bin arayn in shpitol.

433
00:25:59,898 --> 00:26:02,187
hob ikh gehat a shtarkn fiber.

434
00:26:04,843 --> 00:26:09,562
ikh vel aykh epes do dertseyln, se nisht zeyer apetitlekh, ober se iz a fakt.

435
00:26:11,053 --> 00:26:16,937
bin ikh geshlofn un- untn di di pritsh fun gants untn, hob ikh gekrign dort in shpitol,

436
00:26:19,423 --> 00:26:21,527
un

437
00:26:21,853 --> 00:26:23,889
ikh hob gehat zeyer a groysn fiber,

438
00:26:55,468 --> 00:26:58,314
